<br>
To answer the question quadding is the ability to kite 4 mobs at the same time.<br>
<br>
This is, in my opinion, only an option after level 34 with the AoE spell.<br>
<br>
Snare 4, group them close together and nuke them with the AoE. (area of effect)<br>
<br>
There are long and detailed posts in here, take the time to browse the forums.<br>
<br>
Good luck,<br>
<br>
Queyla Beefcake<br>
