<br>
Snare 4, group them close together and nuke them with the AoE. (area of effect)&quot;<br>
<br>
Yes, you really have to be 34 to quad, as the previous AoE nuke is just too small to be usefull.<br>
<br>
And you need to use ensnare, as snare will almost always wear off before you finish the quad. <p><hr>
